Website, Eblast and Social Media Policies for Event Submissions
We are fortunate to have a very active and vibrant community, and we receive a large number of event submissions. To keep our communications with the public effective and manageable, we limit the listing/posting of events on our website, eblast and social media to the following.
Website
Our online calendar of events found at,
mainstreetdeland.org/calendar
, is a way for us to highlight the fun and exciting events that take place in our vibrant downtown. We list MainStreet events and accept submissions from our members for annual events which are free to the public.
These events must take place in Downtown DeLand
. Historic Downtown DeLand lies from Howry Ave to Wisconsin Ave and from Florida Ave to Alabama Ave. All submissions are subject to approval.
Eblast
The MainStreet DeLand Association sends out a once weekly eblast to our members and members of the community who have requested to receive it. We list MainStreet events and accept submissions from our members for events which are free to the public. Priority is given to events presented by local nonprofits. All submissions are subject to approval.
Social Media
MainStreet DeLand Association social media accounts are exclusively dedicated to MainStreet DeLand communications.
To begin the submission process, please review our guidelines and complete the submission form below. Event submissions are sent to
info@mainstreetdeland.org
. All submissions are subject to approval. Due to the high volume of submissions we receive, we cannot guarantee that all events will be listed/posted. Thank you for your cooperation and understanding.
